# Payments Domain – OpenAPI Specification (Contract Overview)

---

# Info

## Title

Payments Domain API

## Description

This API provides operations for initiating, processing, and querying client payments. It acts as the primary interface between upstream systems (Orders, Billing, Subscription) and the Payments Domain.

The API is designed around idempotent, event-driven payment processing with strong consistency for commands and eventual consistency for status updates.

