# Security

## Authentication

* OAuth2 Client Credentials Flow
* API Key (service-to-service communication)

## Authorization

* Role-based access control (RBAC)
* Domain-scoped permissions (Payments.read, Payments.write)

## Security Requirements

* All requests must use HTTPS
* Sensitive data must not be exposed in responses or logs
* Idempotency key required for all payment creation requests

